01:07:24,520 --> 01:07:26,397
THEN HAVE A MEAL WITH ME. IT'S ON ME

1036
01:07:26,480 --> 01:07:29,108
SATURDAY, NOV 30, 2024
MY LOVING DAUGHTER, I MISS YOU

1037
01:07:33,404 --> 01:07:35,281
SUNDAY DEC 8, 2024
I'M SORRY, GA-YUN

1038
01:07:35,364 --> 01:07:37,283
TUESDAY, DEC 31, 2024
I WILL DO MY BEST

1039
01:07:56,010 --> 01:07:58,470
<i>Minister, I think you need to see this.</i>

1040
01:07:58,554 --> 01:07:59,930
<i>I'm sending you a link.</i>

1041
01:08:04,852 --> 01:08:07,354
<i>I'm sure you will remember</i>
<i>the death of a female teacher</i>

1042
01:08:07,897 --> 01:08:10,065
<i>that led to the establishment of the ERPB.</i>

1043
01:08:10,149 --> 01:08:13,652
The current Minister of Education
and head of the ERPB, Choi Gang-seok,

1044
01:08:13,736 --> 01:08:15,863
is the victim's father.

1045
01:08:17,281 --> 01:08:19,366
And Inspector Na Hwa-jin was her fiancé.

1046
01:08:29,335 --> 01:08:30,753
<i>Those investigated by the ERPB,</i>

1047
01:08:30,836 --> 01:08:34,381
<i>Ryu Jun-hyeong of Daehan High,</i>
<i>the students at Guun High-Tech High,</i>

1048
01:08:34,465 --> 01:08:37,885
<i>and Soyeon Girls' High School,</i>
<i>are all students.</i>

1049
01:08:39,595 --> 01:08:40,596
<i>Is it truly possible</i>

1050
01:08:41,305 --> 01:08:44,725
this has nothing to do with
the teacher killed by her student?

1051
01:08:45,309 --> 01:08:49,271
<i>These people are not working</i>
<i>for educational rights.</i>

1052
01:08:50,189 --> 01:08:51,565
<i>It is cruel revenge</i>

1053
01:08:52,691 --> 01:08:55,236
<i>for the death</i>
<i>of their daughter and fiancée.</i>

1054
01:08:57,863 --> 01:08:59,615
It is a personal vendetta.

1055
01:10:20,571 --> 01:10:23,532
Subtitle translation by: Lisa Kim

